{"tid":1363540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳怡係youtube channel公開R課金 一齊報比稅局有人疑似舉漏稅","createTime":"2019-07-25T08:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T08:37:38.000Z","uid":82829,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"16314b32e5bbb099193ad4daa69ac817493ecff3","tid":1363540,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"taxfai@ird.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n舉報疑似有人漏報稅項<br />\n致稅務局：<br />\n<br />\n我要舉報 Chan Wing Yee，懷疑她漏報收入，或隱瞞公司收入。她於其youtube channel 公開募捐，懷疑有稅項漏報。敬請查証。<br />\n<br />\n良好市民上<br />\n<br />\n<em><br />\n另一個方向就係做良好市民<br />\n向稅局舉報懷疑瞞稅既case, <br />\n不過就唔係任何人都可以隨便舉報，<br />\n要有合理懷疑，<br />\n例如前員工懷疑公司有額外收入。<br />\n稅局接到informer case就會開file處理，bank account check，interview等等<br />\n<br />\n呢個方向並不是要玩稅局，<br />\n而係幫稅局確保公司有交足稅。<br />\n舉例，某執葉大狀家人開既補習社有無完整上報所有收入？tvb 廣告商有無誇大廣告開支？文x報有無上報所有收益？<br />\n</em><br />\n[稅局] IRD 員工話你知不合作運動並不是罷交稅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361453</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"835d23b7dcb5ce757b2d5d38b61c5f2d53843087","tid":1363540,"uid":82829,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fG2wAOr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfG2wAOr.png&h=89fb9dbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳怡：元朗被打市民係先撩者賤<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356897</a>"},{"pid":"1e66b4b2debbdb14cac69a5ea465909834f0cadb","tid":1363540,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:15:31.000Z","msg":"send左"},{"pid":"25097c409e49cca2c73fc827400845268a788a21","tid":1363540,"uid":149973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"良好公民<br />\n打擊逃稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966